<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Belampute'n belam chinga,
 Gama a giehpih lai u'n;
 Angel lopi hung kilang in,
 &quot;Lau kiu inla, ngaitiem u,
 Mi tin a di'n Chanchin Pha leh,
 Kipahum tak,
 Ka hun tutsak hi,&quot; a ti.

[V2]
 2. &quot;Hukdampa chuh a hung pieng ta'i,
 Nangu di'n David khuo ah;
 Lal Krista chuh! Lal Krista chuh!
 Ti'n a hung kiko ta a,
 Nausen deihum, A min Maka,
 Lemguotthiempa -
 Kumsawt Pa, Chamna Lal chu.

[V3]
 3. Pathien Cha ahi, 'hung pieng chuh,
 Gilo kei ei tan dingin;
 Pathien in ei hehpih mahmah,
 A Chapa Chang ei pieta'i,
 Amah pakcha'n I kikhawm u'i,
 A min pak in -
 Aw, khawvel la'n hung dim hen.</lyrics>
<title>THE SAVIOUR IS BORN</title>
</song>